Debian Jessie base box, up to date
----------------------------------

Use boostrap-vz [0] from devlopment branch on testing/jessie to
generate an image, using the manifest provided in
bootstrap-vz-manifests/

Syntax : sudo ./bootstrap-vz --debug --log logs bootstrap-vz-manifests/virtualbox-vagrant.manifest.yml

Then upload it to vagrantcloud.

Cf. oberger/debianjessiemini vagrantcloud image for releases.

TODO : use the minimize-size plugin instead of manually trimming the
disk with zeroes.

[0] http://andsens.github.io/bootstrap-vz/
